  <entry>
    <title>使用hexo生成静态网页并由github托管</title>
    <link href="https://kaze.xyz/p/13284/"/>
    <id>https://kaze.xyz/p/13284/</id>
    <published>2019-02-01T03:11:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-04T15:34:03.450Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="环境">环境<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#环境"></a></h2><p>(1) 安装Git</p><p>下载地址：<a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a></p><p>(2) 安装NodeJS</p><p>下载地址：<a href="https://nodejs.org/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/download/</a></p><p>一路next即可</p><h2 id="配置git">配置git<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#配置git"></a></h2><h4 id="设置你的Git-name">设置你的Git name<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#设置你的Git-name"></a></h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">"usename"</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">"email"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="生成SSH秘钥">生成SSH秘钥<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#生成SSH秘钥"></a></h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"you email"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>连续回车即可</p><p>可以在 <code>.ssh</code> 得到两个文件:<code>id_rsa</code> 和 <code>id_rsa.pub</code></p><h2 id="配置-GitHub">配置 GitHub<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#配置-GitHub"></a></h2><h3 id="注册-github">注册 github<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#注册-github"></a></h3><p>地址: <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/</a><br>按照提示注册就可以,邮箱一定要真实(要验证邮箱),否则无法创建存储库</p><h3 id="创建github存储库">创建github存储库<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#创建github存储库"></a></h3><p>仓库的名字要和你的账号对应，如name.github.io<br>然后选择Create repository</p><h3 id="把id-rsa-pub内容复制-添加到GitHub">把<code>id_rsa.pub</code>内容复制,添加到GitHub<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#把id-rsa-pub内容复制-添加到GitHub"></a></h3><div class="article-img"><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/02/01/5c53ac546c0af.png" alt data-zoomable></p></div><h4 id="验证SSH是否生效">验证SSH是否生效<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#验证SSH是否生效"></a></h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看到<code>Hi</code>后面是你的用户名，就说明成功了。</p><h2 id="使用npm安装hexo">使用<code>npm</code>安装hexo<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#使用npm安装hexo"></a></h2><p>(1) 更改npm源为淘宝源以提高速度</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> registry http://registry.npm.taobao.org/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>(2) Install Hexo</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>跳到一个合适的目录,初始化hexo</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>hexo 根目录,执行<code>hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code></p><p>打开<a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000</a>(默认),你就可以看到你的博客的样子了</p><p>你可以使用<kbd>Ctrl+C</kbd>来结束hexo sever</p><blockquote><p>参考链接<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo官方文档</a></p></blockquote><h3 id="Depoy">Depoy<a href="post/搭建hexo博客-一-基本配置#Depoy"></a></h3><p>(1) 修改的<code>\_config.yml</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">- type:</span> <span class="string">git</span>    <span class="comment">#不需要更改</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  repo:</span>     <span class="comment">#存储库地址</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>(2) 使用<code>hexo depoy</code>部署到GitHub</p><p>先在hexo根目录执行,以安装git部署服务</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后执行<code>hexo d</code>推送成功后就可以 让你的站点被其他人访问了</p><p>地址是:youusename.github.io</p>]]></content>
    
